# React components

## Functions

- Use **arrow functions** for components and hooks — avoid `export function` for React code.
- Type exported components with **`React.FC<Props>`** when they accept props (see `LoginForm`, `CardContainer`, `UserProvider`).
- Props: named `ComponentNameProps` or `T…` for shared types (`TDefaultDialogFormPublicProps`).
- Zero-prop components may omit `React.FC` (`ThemeToggle`, simple pages).

```tsx
// ✅
type LoginFormProps = TDefaultDialogFormPublicProps;
export const LoginForm: React.FC<LoginFormProps> = ({ forDialog = false }) => { … };

// ❌
export function LoginForm({ forDialog }: LoginFormProps) { … }
```

## File naming & placement

| Suffix / path | Purpose |
|---------------|---------|
| `*.page.tsx` in `pages/` | Route screens (`LoginPage`, `HomePage`) |
| `*.layout.tsx` in `pages/` | Layout shells wired in routes (`Root.layout.tsx`) |
| `*.form.tsx` | Feature forms (`login.form.tsx`) |
| `*.field.tsx` in `form/fields/` | TanStack Form field components |
| `routes/*.tsx` | Thin TanStack Router files — export `Route` only |
| `components/ui/` | shadcn primitives — do not hand-roll duplicates |

## UI & styling

- Merge classes with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`.
- Use existing shadcn components under `@/components/ui/`.
- Icons: `lucide-react`.
- Router links/navigation: `Link`, `useNavigate` from `@tanstack/react-router`.

## Forms (feature forms)

- Zod schema: `const FooSchema = z.object({…})` with `import z from "zod"`.
- `useAppForm` + `DefaultForm` + `form.AppField` + `FieldGroup` / `FieldSet`.
- Submit loading: local `isPending` / `isSuccess` + `form.SubmitButton`.

## Exceptions

- **Generic** components may use untyped/generic arrows (`DefaultForm`, `DefaultField`) instead of `React.FC`.
- **Route files** export `Route`; `react-refresh/only-export-components` allows this.
